Name: Seismic Toss
Effect: Roll Fighting-Type Damage Dice according to the User's Rank: Starter/1 Die; Rookie/2 Dice; Standard/4 Dice; Advanced/6 Dice; Expert/8 Dice; Ace or higher/10 Dice. Ignore Defenses.
Description: The target gets launched up, then falls face first into the ground. The stronger the user, the higher the foe will be thrown.
